```plantuml
@startuml Crazy0416_KnowledgeGraph

actor User
participant "UI Component" as UI
participant "Search Controller" as SearchCtrl
participant "Graph Controller" as GraphCtrl
participant "Sigma.js Renderer" as Sigma
participant "Elasticsearch" as ES
participant "CayleyGraph" as Cayley

User -> UI : Enter search query
UI -> SearchCtrl : processSearch(query)
SearchCtrl -> ES : queryRDFData(query)
ES --> SearchCtrl : RDF results
SearchCtrl -> Cayley : fetchGraphRelationships(results)
Cayley --> SearchCtrl : Graph data
SearchCtrl -> GraphCtrl : updateGraph(data)
GraphCtrl -> Sigma : renderGraph(nodes, edges)
Sigma --> GraphCtrl : Rendering complete
GraphCtrl --> UI : Display visualization
UI --> User : Show knowledge graph

User -> UI : Interact with graph (e.g. drag node)
UI -> GraphCtrl : handleInteraction(event)
GraphCtrl -> Sigma : updateLayout()
Sigma --> GraphCtrl : Layout updated
GraphCtrl --> UI : Update display
UI --> User : Show updated graph

User -> UI : Request pathfinding
UI -> GraphCtrl : findPath(start, end)
GraphCtrl -> Sigma : calculateAStarPath(start, end)
Sigma --> GraphCtrl : Path result
GraphCtrl --> UI : Display path
UI --> User : Show highlighted path

@enduml
```